Xinhua News Agency , UN , April 4 ( Reporter Ding Baozhong ) Bertini , UN World Food Program ( WFP ) Executive Director , said on the 4th in New York that WFP distributed a total of nearly 1.7 billion US dollars worth of food aid in various parts of the world in 2001 and has become the largest humanitarian aid agency in the world .
